HEADWORD: Tampoe
<hw>Tam"poe</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The
edible fruit of an East Indian tree (<spn>Baccaurea Malayana</spn>) of
the Spurge family. It somewhat resembles an apple.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

